Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only after arriving to a big city,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that drakers can finally stretch\Ntheir legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a brief moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why,\Nit becomes an irreplaceable memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to impose on you\Nfor dinner as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, we have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry again, he always sleeps\Nas soon as he drinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always so sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see he hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when he drinks\Nwith Gramps Ura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stupidly strong with alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Quin Zaza leaving soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still repairs to do so\NI think we'll stay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be able to see the\Nfestival the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, there's a festival?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.07,0:01:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.91,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that... it's smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... a fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That way's the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Takita, let's go.\N-Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk... and we just got here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Crocco-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a call for rescue,\Nthey're on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do with the Zaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayne, you go wake up the old man Dag
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and warm up the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Capella, go to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it so we can move it at any given time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we gotta save the vacation for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what have you done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,E... evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's someone hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, what way do we run to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll lend you a hand.\NHang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't finish it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've taken down dragons that big\Ncountless times before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It suddenly started moving when\Nwe got back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there are dragons out there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,much tougher than we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't use enough for it to be lethal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... we used a whole lot of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ship we shoot poison\Nto capture dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For that dragon too, we let it\Nfall to the ground and towed it after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't mind the details now,\Nhelping people comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, before the dragon\Nstarts rampaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie! Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He would've been happier if he\Nkicked the bucket just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When my time comes please\Ndo it to me, Vannie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We need help over here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there a dragon inside the city...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... and it's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna charge into the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,City guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get any closer\Nto the town areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't shoot at random!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,G... good! Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't care, attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The city is... on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate the citizens outside the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to evacuate too, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the first time I see\None like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you got your heart stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find a good man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you understand, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whimsical dreams will be your demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're evacuating, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are we supposed to evacuate to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They said a dragon is on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter if this place goes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be the same everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have anywhere to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the drakers doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it's precisely their ship\Nthat they can't use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...\Nand the mess they did today too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of them,\Nwe can't do business in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll be going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You take refuge soon too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No festival for us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... the merchant ships are all gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get going as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's going to happen\Nto the people of this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That dragon has stopped moving\Nfor now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if we get\Ninvolved in its frenzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna end up like that big ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw that heat ray and blast,\Ndidn't you, Takita?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, we couldn't possibly\Ndo anything with a dragon that huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mika isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was with us until a moment ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk... what's he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He can only be thinking about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, I'm sorry but could you\Nget Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we take the townspeople on board\Nthe Quin Zaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them on board for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, I undersand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, come on, we can't stay here\Nwasting time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't fly anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps Ura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They used poison, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I can tell from the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And to make it worse,\Nit lost its sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what's\Ndeeper than the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's people's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine and all, but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,can we eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs! We can carry the people to\Nthe neighbouring town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about the only ship that's left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not realistic, I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You say "the neighbouring town"\Nbut it's still pretty far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How many round trips do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, this is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a problem between that ship that brought\Na half-dead dragon and this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not being your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you been-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We can eat that dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! So happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,E-eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... you're one of a kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just talking about\Ngetting out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was people's actions that hurt\Nthe dragon to that extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it should also be people's\Nactions that put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally, humans and nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can extract the poison\Nfrom its meat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:14:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the type of poison, but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there is always a method.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He says we can eat that huge thing!\NHear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "hear it?" us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I... think it's fine if\Nwe capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we had encountered
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,something that big in the sky,\Nwe wouldn't have been able to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wounded dragon,\Nwhich has fallen to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we said earlier, we're outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fail,\Nno one will put the blame on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes wrong,\Nwe can just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes well, the benefits\Nare for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially, for a poor ship like ours,\Nthe only chance to catch something this big
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is now. Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you calling a poor ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of a way to catch that dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are we doing it, Crocco-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's come to this,\Nwhat else we gotta do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be poor but we have\Nexperience and intuition going for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll teach the rest of the ship crews\Na lesson or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One last big catch before our vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're drakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to an agreement with\Nthe other ship's captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to lend us some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the memorandum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he give you trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain's a calm person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew didn't seem satisfied though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the one who packed these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't put the\Nbullets and gunpowder in pairs,\Nwe can't use them right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,'ight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, we're just going to attack it\Nboth from land and the air at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you call that a strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... sure that's not\Nexperience nor intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, things will go however they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they go wrong, that'd be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... if that happens\Nsay goodbye to the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we are alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time to talk,\Nmove your hands instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the one loading the guns, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to know what's in the cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeees.\N-Hey, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? What.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know when will the dragon\Nstart rampaging again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro-san is very enthusiastic today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I loaded the harpoon gun with\Ndouble the gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It should do quite a lot of damage\Nif it explodes inside the dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you splurged there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you if you fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it work, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs! We're almost done preparing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go over the plan again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An autogyro! How rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys from the other ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys... what do they intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing this didn't burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our prey, to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To think he accepted their proposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our captain's not right in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I could let them take\N300 barrels of dragon oil from\Nunder our noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finish it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What have they done...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to go wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Those idiots! They ran off on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're starting as soon as possible!\NTell those down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a hurry, please make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Katja!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
